Interface ResourceGroup

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Indexable, Refreshable<ResourceGroup>, Resource, Updatable<ResourceGroup.Update>, Wrapper<ResourceGroupInner>

    public interface ResourceGroup
extends Indexable, Resource, Refreshable<ResourceGroup>, Wrapper<ResourceGroupInner>, Updatable<ResourceGroup.Update>
    An immutable client-side representation of an Azure resource group.
